<h2>Refresh Tiddler</h2>
[img class="tc-image-documentation" [$:/ipfs/image/view/refresh]]
<p>
  The <b>refresh</b> action reloads the current Tiddler.
</p>
<p>
  It implements the following behaviour:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Imported Tiddlers are reloaded.</li>
  <li>
    External attachments are reloaded.
    It is a useful behaviour when you declined to unencrypt an encrypted external resource.
    The unencrypt password dialog box will be displayed again.
  </li>
  <li>
    Regular Tiddler are removed from the <b>~TiddlyWiki</b> cache and reloaded.
    It is a useful behaviour when you want to load content from a different IPFS gateway.
  </li>
  <li>[[Imported|Import]] Tiddlers are reloaded.</li>
</ul>